Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:37.83,ed - cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}奇蹟的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:41.88,ed - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}あなたへ捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:41.88,ed - cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}一切都獻給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:44.21,ed - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}涙のバタフライ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:44.21,ed - cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}淚光的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:46.34,ed - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}眩しいバタフライ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:46.34,ed - cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}耀眼的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:53.68,ed - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}全てが　今書き換えられる
